Class Vector<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

java.lang.Object
Vector<E>
public class Vector<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
The Vector class is based on an array but has a number of useful features such as the ability to extend its capacity. It is a generic class that can take the type contained as an argument.
